# Obsidian Vault - Git Sync Rules
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# Purpose: Define which Obsidian files should sync to GitHub
# Last Updated: 2025-11-07
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# KEEP THESE FILES (Sync to GitHub)
# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Keep plugin configurations (helps team sync settings)
!.obsidian/plugins/

# Keep community plugin list (so team installs same plugins)
!.obsidian/community-plugins.json

# Keep plugin setup documentation
!.obsidian/plugins-setup.md

# Keep appearance settings (consistent theme across team)
!.obsidian/appearance.json

# Keep hotkey configurations (consistent shortcuts)
!.obsidian/hotkeys.json

# Keep graph settings (visual doctrine connections)
!.obsidian/graph.json

# Keep template folder (for new doctrine creation)
!.obsidian/templates/

# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# IGNORE THESE FILES (Don't sync to GitHub)
# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Workspace snapshots (personal layouts, window positions)
workspace*
.obsidian/workspace.json
.obsidian/workspace-mobile.json

# Cache files (auto-generated, personal)
.obsidian/cache
.obsidian/workspace-cache

# Plugin data directories (contain personal state)
.obsidian/plugins/*/data.json

# Sync plugin conflicts (if using Obsidian Sync)
.obsidian/sync-conflict-*

# Local graph settings (personal view preferences)
.obsidian/graph-local.json

# File recovery (auto-saved drafts)
.obsidian/.trash/

# Daily notes cache (if using Periodic Notes)
.obsidian/daily-notes-cache.json

# Backups (if using backup plugins)
.obsidian/backups/

# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# RATIONALE
# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# ✅ Sync plugin configs → Team uses same plugins
# ✅ Sync templates → Consistent doctrine creation
# ✅ Sync appearance → Consistent visual experience
# ❌ Don't sync workspace → Personal window layouts
# ❌ Don't sync cache → Auto-generated, personal
# ❌ Don't sync plugin data → Personal plugin state

# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# VERIFICATION
# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# To see what's being ignored:
#   git status --ignored
#
# To force-add an ignored file:
#   git add -f .obsidian/workspace.json
#
# To check specific file status:
#   git check-ignore -v .obsidian/workspace.json
